    "type": "markdown",
    "source": "# ML: Player Churn Prediction Model\n\nThis notebook builds a machine learning model to predict player churn risk\nusing the Gold layer player 360 data.\n\n## Model Approach:\n- Binary classification (churned vs active)\n- Gradient Boosted Trees classifier\n- MLflow experiment tracking\n- Feature importance analysis"
